{"entry_type":"decision","summary":"Notification system uses pure event-driven architecture via EventBus with pluggable NotificationAdapter pattern","detail":"EventBus was already the primary pattern in the codebase with typed events, event logging, and async support. The codebase comments explicitly flagged the mixed pattern as tech debt. EventBus provides: (1) loose coupling between services and notification delivery, (2) typed event payloads via AppEvent union, (3) event log for debugging/testing, (4) easy addition of new event subscribers without modifying emitters. The adapter pattern on the delivery side enables adding new channels (webhook, SMS, in-app) without modifying NotificationService.","tags":["architecture"],"scope":"src/services/notification.service.ts","agent_id":"agent-1","id":"01KN8RKGTCCGZFGZZK6H1JKWNS","timestamp":"2026-04-03T04:11:16.172Z"}
